Stero type annotation

Controller --->>> for controller
Repository --->>> for dao
Service --->> for business
component ---> non mvc classes >> utill class 

   		
<context:annotation-config> activates

(@Autowired)AutowiredAnnotationBeanPostProcessor and (@Required)RequiredAnnotationBeanPostProcessor
@PostConstruct @Predestroy
   		
@component will b used th create the object of the class that is having the only secondary type object...

we have to manually create the object by using property tag if class is having primary tag.